MULTIPLE OFFERS RECEIVED DEADLINE 11-3 AT 12 PM, SELLER WILL ONLY CONSIDER THE BEST AND HIGHEST OFFER.
Welcome to this lovely, well-maintained home, conveniently located near retail shopping, grocery stores, and a variety of dining options. With great access to the highway, your commute will be a breeze. This home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths, all under just a bit under 2000 sqFt. The beautiful laminate and tile flooring run throughout, adding a touch of elegance. The living room and kitchen offer plenty of space for entertaining or just relaxing. Ideal for first-time home buyers, this property is more than just a house, it's a home. Ask the agent about the Bank of America program offering 100% free down payment assistance, with no credit requirement and much more. Don't miss out on this opportunity, contact us today to take a tour of this beauty.
